{"word":"G4139 - πλησίον - plēsíon - play-see'-on - Near","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">πλησίον</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">plēsíon</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">play-see'-on</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Near</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adverb / வினையடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"அடுத்தவன், பிறன், அயலான் - வினையடை"},{"paragraph":"a neighbor, friend"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Neuter of a derivative of <b>&#x03C0;&#x03B5;&#x0301;&#x03BB;&#x03B1;&#x03C2;</b> <b>pelas</b> (<i>near</i>); (adverb) <i>close</i> by; as noun, a <i>neighbor</i>, that is, <i>fellow</i> (as man, countryman, Christian or friend): - near, neighbour.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}